snippet.title: Shotgun Farmers - Launch Trailer - A Game By QaziTV
snippet.description:
Shotgun Farmers is the multiplayer shooter where missed shots grow guns!
🎮 Available now on Steam: http://bit.ly/shotgunfarmers
🎮 Pre-Order for Xbox One: http://bit.ly/shotgunfarmersxbox

Shotgun Farmers is the first-person multiplayer shooter where missed shots grow guns. Reloading isn’t an option, so grab one of the deadly crops planted by earlier missed shots. Shot at by a sniper? Well they just planted you your very own sniper gun to fire back with! Harvest weapon plants quickly for more ammo or let them grow for a larger clip. 

Join our Discord server: https://discord.gg/shotgunfarmers

🎮 Steam: http://bit.ly/shotgunfarmers
🎮 Xbox One: http://bit.ly/shotgunfarmersxbox
🌐 Official Website: https://www.shotgunfarmers.com
🖤 Follow Shotgun Farmers on TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@qazitv
🖤 Follow Shotgun Farmers on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ShotgunFarmers
🖤 Like Shotgun Farmers on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ShotgunFarmers

#indiegame #fpsgame #shotgunfarmers
